Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,807)\fade(501,0)\t(0,0,\fscx120,\fscy120)}Matsumoto Meets Michael Jackson
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"We're told Michael Jackson is due to visit Japan soon...."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"....given that Matsumoto-san and Michael Jackson are such good friends..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"....is it true that MJ hangs out with Matsumoto-san at his house whenever he visits Japan?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say Michael and I go back a long way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,....back to the time he made his earlier trip to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Was it a chance first encounter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, I went to see him in concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so special about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that was just how it all began!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the front row!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Michael sensed something special in me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the several ten-thousands in the audience, I guess he was struck by how I was looking at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I really stood out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can really tell, 'This guy's a hard-core fan!'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The intensity with which I was watching his act must have carried through to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was from the second half of the show that Michael would just stand right in front of me....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...and do THIS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when he started visiting me, and hanging out with me at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but the guy wants to know what the two of you would be up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he would help out around the house in many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for example - when I would be doing the dishes, he would be waiting next to me patiently with a towel to dry them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, for sure! - and then when I'd have to lift something heavy like a table....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...Michael would stand at the other end, and give me a hand picking it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such great guy, and pretty handy that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when you had to make those tricky maneuvers with long items of furniture....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...Michael would know exactly how far to back up before swerving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This one time, Michael backed so far up, it was just amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't make sudden, sharp turns with those long tables, otherwise - BANG! - you'll end up banging your elbow against the wall, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael wouldn't do that - he'd go back all the way, and THEN make the turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He really got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I realized just how supremely awesome the guy really was!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That IS pretty awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:02:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna know something else? - we both have the same tastes, Michael and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely, SPOT ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We even laugh at the same things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How come he laughs at everything you find funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, say for example, when you serve a bowl of hot miso soup, and then set it on the table....?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,....and the bowl starts to slide, and it makes that funny slipping sound sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We just like totally crack up at that, Michael and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he does that famous 'hoo-hoo-hooooo' yell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, it's a riot!

